snippet.title: Cities: Skylines Park Life Release Trailer
snippet.description:
More Play, Less Stress - Cities: Skylines - Parklife is Available Now! 
Steam: https://pdxint.at/2IFXjD1
Plaza: https://pdxint.at/2x7ST2o

Cities: Skylines now offers vibrant new parks, playgrounds, zoos, green spaces and more importantly, new ways to play. With a new park area tool, five new maps, a ton of new assets and level-up features that increase your park’s property values, Parklife is will spruce up any city in a snap.
